      "weather": "Overcast",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TICKETS (8) has been a little hard to follow, missing the frame last time but was a Grade 5 winner three back and returns to 410m where he tends to run well. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. MORE BEER PLEASE (2) showed blistering pace early and gave a sight when in the minors, beaten 2.5 lengths over 410m this track in 23.72. Expecting another good run. WHOPPI DEVERE (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (24.39) in a Grade 5 at Bendigo. Has a good record at this journey. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Cannot be underestimated. ASTON FINNISS (1) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
